oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Proceedings of the Twenty-Second Annual Conference (1989). Opening Ceremony
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The 22nd Annual Meeting in the heartland of America will be remembered for a long time for its family atmosphere and an outstanding scientific program. The opening ceremony on Tuesday, November 14 was preceeded by a typical AABP reunion of friends and meeting new ones at the sumptuous "happy hour" a buffet in true Kansas City Style at the Convention Center.
